<p>
</p>
<h3>
	吴冠中系列纹样餐具 by Z-Inhouse
</h3>
<p>
	成立于 2014 年 9 月的造作很喜欢使用色彩，这是他们独立出来的设计团队 Z-Inhouse 推出的吴冠中系列纹样餐具。有红色和黄色两组，分别使用了吴冠中的《印尼舟群》和《白桦林》两幅画作纹样，陶瓷碗里面装饰以明媚鲜艳的红色和黄色，富有非常强烈的艺术气息。售价 199 元起，<a href="http://zaozuo.com/item/300050" target="_blank">这里分别是红色款</a>和<a href="http://zaozuo.com/item/300054" target="_blank">黄色款的购买链接。</a> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/27dc8601e268.jpg" width="1080" height="608" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/babfaf89991f.jpg" width="1080" height="608" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/75e1b35e94ae.jpg" width="1080" height="608" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/13ddf89c7ccd.jpg" width="1080" height="608" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/103e9a2311bf.jpg" width="1080" height="608" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/be64411ab4dd.jpg" width="1080" height="608" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<h3>
	The Ultimate Suitcase by Jurni
</h3>
<p>
	这是一个专为年轻人设计的旅行箱，它可以承受 200 斤以内的人坐在上面。箱子的最上面可以直接打开，放一些随身的电子产品，也可以拆下的当做盒子带到另外的地方。打开箱子后，里面有一块可移动的板，将箱子的内部空间分成上下两部分，成为一个带两个格子的柜子。有红、蓝、粉三种颜色可选，<a href="http://www.indiegogo.com/projects/jurni-the-ultimate-sit-on-carry-on-suitcase#/" target="_blank">这里是众筹链接。</a> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/e7b631a1c693.jpg" width="620" height="413" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/d1afc8b05de7.jpg" width="620" height="413" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/dc46f44e8dcb.jpg" width="620" height="314" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/33bd324448b0.jpg" width="620" height="413" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/b79b703bd8c8.jpg" width="620" height="332" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/d36844850467.jpg" width="620" height="197" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<h3>
	LEVIT8 by Levit8 Co.
</h3>
<p>
	这是一个专门放笔记本的折叠桌面，专为办公室人群设计。折叠之前，它是一个笔记本的保护壳，按照纹路交叉旋转后可以成为一个立体的台面，方便久坐的人站起来使用。如果遇到过矮茶几，也能帮你调整视线，更舒服地使用电脑。它是用压克力帆布做的，有大小三种型号，目前正在众筹，<a href="http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1459624267/levit8-the-first-truly-portable-standing-desk" target="_blank">这里是众筹链接。</a> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/ed8044921705.gif" width="680" height="378" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/d028bec88aaf.jpg" width="800" height="533" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/620a5bd05d95.jpg" width="680" height="454" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/7cde20f2f4d6.jpg" width="800" height="533" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/d7fe632ef020.jpg" width="800" height="533" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/1025be2ff276.jpg" width="680" height="454" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<h3>
	Autoprogettazione furniture by Enzo Mari&nbsp;
</h3>
<p>
	这是意大利的设计大师 Enzo Mari 在 1974 年设计的 Autoprogrettazione 系列，购买者需要自己用锤子和钉子组装，以此来让人们更多地参与到家具设计中。他将这一系列的版权出售给了 CUCULA ，即西非手工艺设计计划，允许他们重新设计出售，以获得更多的资金帮助贫困地区。自己参与的概念也能鼓励当地人用木板为自己制作家具。
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/aa33f24d2e59.jpg" width="784" height="560" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/06c9056d9f61.jpg" width="936" height="624" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/07ebf934b8a7.jpg" width="936" height="644" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/2e2e1fe2432e.jpg" width="936" height="628" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/31e5d6bf7728.jpg" width="936" height="624" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p>
	<span></span> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<h3>
	Chandon Holiday by ButterlyCannon
</h3>
<p>
	ButterflyCannon 是一家专为时尚精品店做设计的事务所，他们曾为Chandon 设计过多种包装。这次的假期主题主要用了香槟的颜色，在白色的胶套上面印满了手写粗体文字，大小不一，自由而活泼。其余的说明文字用了黑体，显得正式。香槟色本身带有一种时尚和优雅，在白色的映衬下显得简洁大方。<span></span> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/bd9f5ec5e9b8.jpg" width="538" height="596" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/e4bd7d7452c8.jpg" width="538" height="622" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/653723fb4552.jpg" width="538" height="303" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/57dbd9c4c872.jpg" width="538" height="807" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
